🔒 Privacy & Security:
What GitHub Sees:
❌ No audio data
❌ No spoken words
❌ No user input
✅ Only file download requests (who visits the page)
What Google Sees:
✅ Audio data (for transcription)
✅ Spoken words
❌ No personal information (unless you speak it)
What Stays Local:
✅ Target words entered
✅ Comparison results
✅ All calculations
